  "StockRole": "Scout",
  "YangsThoughts": "Hellespont named this one after a MechWarrior operating in Capellan space, which tells you what kind of machine it was meant to be. The Partial Wing came from Jade Falcon hardware, the MML from a mercenary company. Maggie Faraday herself raided one in 3069 and ran it for decades. After the Jihad the CCAF sold a limited number to mercenaries working with the Magistracy. Whatever you paid for this one, it was worth it.",
